{
  "id": "adv_main_04_10_04",
  "title": "星空編1章49話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブバトルが終わって数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_backstage-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.4666666905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんが帰った後のステージ……\nライブの時の熱気が嘘みたいに静かだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7135828257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきまで、私はここで歌ってたんだよね\nここでリズノワに勝ったんだよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.488163813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "無我夢中だったせいかな？\nなんだか夢を見ていたような気分だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.6666666,
          "startTime": 27.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.9467123907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "夢じゃないわ\nさくらはこのステージでリズノワに勝ったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.5871199848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん！？\nどうしてここに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2080497346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてじゃないでしょ。楽屋に挨拶しに行ったら\nさくらがいないから探し回ったんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6227458343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、さくらはここで何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6053514404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.3982312921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "どうやってリズノワに勝てたのか……\n忘れないうちに、今日のステージを振り返ろうと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7207511031
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 54.7540844382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらは最初、調子が悪かったわよね？\nなのに途中から急に動きが良くなった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、さくらの身に何が起こったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2776902601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.9017039542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "それが、自分でもよく分からないんだ。前半の私は\n体が思うように動かなくて、みんなの足を引っ張ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃ私のせいでサニピが負ける……\n嫌だ、負けたくない……みんなと勝ちたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6900933282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.5773536609
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 94.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そう強く願ったら、心臓がドクンって跳ねたの\n力強く鼓動を刻んで、体の奥から力が湧いてきたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6000048321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7806465394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことが……\nでも、どうして急に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4666760764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.1713516799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら、麻奈さんが私の想いに応えて\n力を貸してくれたのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8333447776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "私が感じた鼓動は、麻奈さんが起こした\n一度きりの奇跡なんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.566678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.3722117671
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 122.2666765851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……それはどうかしら。お姉ちゃんなら、サニピと\nリズノワの真剣勝負に割って入ることはしないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3333432517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.1012595742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、歌声もその心臓も、もうさくらのものよ\n今更、都合良くお姉ちゃんが出て来たりしないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3000099184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.3341163566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "だからきっと、今日の奇跡はさくらの積み重ねてきた\n努力と、勝利への強い想いが起こした必然よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5000099184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.1815130712
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのかな……。それでも私は、麻奈さんは\n今でもどこかで見守ってくれていると思いたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2000129702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん私も、困った時は麻奈さんが\n助けてくれるなんて、期待してないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.5015593751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.9555711678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "奇跡を当てにして自分で頑張らないアイドルを\n麻奈さんは助けたりしないと思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3333463035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.2171812307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。助けてくれるかは別にして\nお姉ちゃんなら、きっとどこかで私達を見ているわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.1000129702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.3599472613
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
